<% layout('layouts/boilerplate')%>
<div class="container-fluid p-5">
  <h3>HOW TO POST AD IN OLX</h3>
  <ul class="fs-5">
    <li><b>Step 1:</b>First login to your Gmail using Gmail id & password.</li>
    <img src="../images/marketing-d1a.png" alt="" />
    <img src="../images/marketing-d1b.png" alt="" />
    <li>
      <b>Step 2:</b> Next, open the site Olx.in. Then click on the login option.
    </li>
    <img src="../images/marketing-d2.png" alt="" />
    <li>
      <b>Step 3:</b>After click on the login option, you see more 4 option.
      Click on anyone according to your convenience. ( It provides 4 options to
      log in like Facebook, Google, Phone, Email). Just click on “CONTINUE WITH
      EMAIL”You will see the option to enter your email. Just fill it with your
      email id & click on next.
    </li>
    <img src="../images/marketing-d3.png" alt="" />
    <img src="../images/marketing-d3a.png" alt="" />

    <li>
      <b>Step 4:</b>After clicking on the Next button, it will ask for OTP which
      will come on your email id. Fill the 4 digit OTP in the box.
    </li>
    <img src="../images/marketing-d4.png" alt="" />
    <li>
      <b>Step 5:</b>After filling the 4 digit OTP, click on login button. When
      you clicked on login it will ask to create a password. (Save it for login
      all the time).
    </li>
    <img src="../images/marketing-d5.png" alt="" />
    <li>
      <b>Step 6:</b>After filling the password part click on CREATE PASSWORD
      button. After creating the password you will redirect on another page,
      where you can upload your profile pictures.
    </li>
    <img src="../images/marketing-d6.png" alt="" />
    <li>
      <b>Step 7:</b>After uploading the profile pictures click on the CONTINUE ,
      When you click on continue, it will ask for your Mobile number.
    </li>
    <img src="../images/marketing-d7.png" alt="" />
    <li>
      <b>Step 8:</b>Enter your mobile number & click on CONTINUE. Then an OTP
      will come on your mobile number
    </li>
    <img src="../images/marketing-d8.png" alt="" />
    <li>
      <b>Step 9:</b>After filling the mobile OTP click on CONTINUE. Now you have
      completed your registration.
    </li>
    <img src="../images/marketing-d9.png" alt="" />
    <li>
      <b>Step 10:</b>After clicking on the SELL option, this is highlighted in
      blue colour in the right corner.
    </li>
    <img src="../images/marketing-d10.png" alt="" />
    <li>
      <b>Step 11:</b> When you click on the sell option you will see category
      option & many sub-categories, from there you have to select your category
      & sub-categories in which you want to submit your products & services.
    </li>
    <img src="../images/marketing-d11.png" alt="" />
    <li>
      <b>Step 12:</b>After selecting category & sub-categories you will redirect
      on a page to post your ads. Fill the required details & click post now
      option to finish. After filling all details click on POST NOW.
    </li>
    <img src="../images/marketing-d12.png" alt="" />
  </ul>
</div>
